{
  "abstract": "The 1973-74 season has been a year of great expansion for the Farming Systems Program at ICRISAT both in terms of staff and with regards to the scope of the program. Six Research Assistants joined the farming systems team. A number of catchments were developed and the watershed-based phase of the program was initiated...",
